rk with", "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.headertitle", "pk": 4, "fields": {"title": "My Projects", "subtitle": "Some of the work I’ve built and contributed to", "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.headertitle", "pk": 5, "fields": {"title": "Contact Me", "subtitle": "Feel free to reach out for opportunities or collaborations", "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.herosection", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "Geeta R Galagali", "subtitle": "Full Stack Developer | AI/ML Enthusiast", "image": "hero/geeta.webp", "resume": "resumes/Geeta_R_Galagali_resume.pdf", "is_active": true, "projects_count": 5, "clients_count": 0, "experience_count": 3}}, {"model": "main.quote", "pk": 1, "fields": {"text": "Passionate about building impactful solutions through technology and continuous learning.", "display_order": 0, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.aboutsection", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "About Me", "content": "I am a final-year Information Science Engineering student with a strong foundation in Data Structures, Web Development, and AI-based applications. I have hands-on experience building real-world projects using Django, React, and Machine Learning through internships and academic work.\r\n\r\nI am passionate about solving problems and continuously improving my technical skills. I enjoy working on full-stack applications and exploring new technologies like AI/ML and iOS development.\r\n\r\nMy goal is to secure a challenging role where I can apply my skills, grow as a developer, and contribute to impactful solutions.", "section_type": "focus", "display_order": 0, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.timelineitem", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "B.E. in Information Science Engineering", "period": "2023 – 2027", "description": "Currently pursuing my Bachelor's degree with a CGPA of 8.79. Building strong foundations in Data Structures, Web Development, DBMS, and Operating Systems.", "category": "education", "display_order": 0, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.timelineitem", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "AI Solutions Intern – EDUNET Foundation (Microsoft Azure)", "period": "May 2025 – Jun 2025", "description": "Developed an AI chatbot using Django and Hugging Face for real-time question answering. Implemented NLP-based response generation and presented the project outcome.", "category": "career", "display_order": 1, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.timelineitem", "pk": 3, "fields": {"title": "AI/ML Intern – Employability.life", "period": "Aug 2025 – Sep 2025", "description": "Worked on a Cancer Prediction System using machine learning models. Contributed to data preprocessing, synthetic data generation, and model training for improved prediction accuracy.", "category": "career", "display_order": 2, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.timelineitem", "pk": 4, "fields": {"title": "AI/ML Virtual Intern – Infosys Springboard", "period": "Aug 2025 – Sep 2025", "description": "Developed an NLU-based chatbot by preprocessing datasets and training machine learning models for intent recognition. Evaluated model performance and compared accuracy metrics to select the best model.", "category": "career", "display_order": 3, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.skill", "pk": 1, "fields": {"name": "Data Structures & Algorithms", "proficiency": 80, "icon_class": "fas fa-code", "display_order": 0, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.skill", "pk": 2, "fields": {"name": "Django", "proficiency": 85, "icon_class": "fab fa-python", "display_order": 1, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.skill", "pk": 3, "fields": {"name": "React.js", "proficiency": 75, "icon_class": "fab fa-react", "display_order": 2, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.skill", "pk": 4, "fields": {"name": "Python", "proficiency": 80, "icon_class": "fab fa-python", "display_order": 3, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.skill", "pk": 5, "fields": {"name": "C++", "proficiency": 75, "icon_class": "fas fa-code", "display_order": 4, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.skill", "pk": 6, "fields": {"name": "MySQL", "proficiency": 70, "icon_class": "fas fa-database", "display_order": 5, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.skill", "pk": 7, "fields": {"name": "HTML, CSS & JavaScript", "proficiency": 75, "icon_class": "fab fa-js", "display_order": 6, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.skill", "pk": 8, "fields": {"name": "AI / Machine Learning", "proficiency": 70, "icon_class": "fas fa-brain", "display_order": 7, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.certificate", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "SQL and Relational Databases 101", "issuer": "IBM (CognitiveClass.ai)", "description": "Completed certification on SQL fundamentals, database design, and relational database concepts.", "image": "certificates/Screenshot_2026-04-01_012107.webp", "issue_date": "2025-05-10", "display_order": 0, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.certificate", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "Cybersecurity Essentials", "issuer": "IBM SkillBuild", "description": "Learned fundamental concepts of cybersecurity including network security, threats, vulnerabilities, and best practices for securing systems.", "image": "certificates/Cybersecurity_Fundamentals_2.webp", "issue_date": "2025-06-18", "display_order": 1, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.project", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "AI-Powered Career Guidance Portal", "description": "Developed an AI-based career guidance platform using Django that helps users identify suitable career paths through interactive quizzes and progress tracking.\r\n\r\nImplemented recommendation logic to analyze user responses and suggest personalized career options. Designed authentication system and user-friendly interface for better engagement.\r\n\r\nTech Stack: Django, Html, CSS, Python, SQLite", "technologies": "Django, HTML, CSS, Python, SQLite", "demo_link": "https://github.com/Geeta1923/ai-career-guidance-portal", "github_link": "https://github.com/Geeta1923", "display_order": 0, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.project", "pk": 2, "fields": {"title": "E-commerce Web Application", "description": "Developed a full-stack e-commerce platform using React and Django REST Framework with features like user authentication, product management, and shopping cart functionality.\r\n\r\nIntegrated Razorpay payment gateway for secure transactions and order processing. Designed RESTful APIs for seamless frontend-backend communication and optimized database operations using MySQL.\r\n\r\nTech Stack: React.js, Django REST Framework, Python, MySQL, Razorpay API", "technologies": "React.js, Django REST Framework, Python, MySQL, Razorpay API", "demo_link": "https://github.com/Geeta1923/ecommerce-django-react", "github_link": "https://github.com/Geeta1923", "display_order": 1, "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.projectimage", "pk": 1, "fields": {"project": 1, "image": "projects/Screenshot_2025-12-21_233443.webp", "alt_text": "AI Career Guidance Portal Screenshot", "display_order": 0}}, {"model": "main.projectimage", "pk": 2, "fields": {"project": 2, "image": "projects/Screenshot_2026-02-23_220601.webp", "alt_text": "E-commerce Web Application Screenshot", "display_order": 1}}, {"model": "main.contactmessage", "pk": 1, "fields": {"name": "Geeta Rayappa Galagali", "email": "geetagalagali05@gmail.com", "message": "hi", "created_at": "2026-04-01T18:43:32.167Z", "is_read": false}}, {"model": "main.contactinfo", "pk": 1, "fields": {"title": "Get In Touch", "description": "I am currently open to internship and full-time opportunities in software development and AI/ML. Feel free to reach out for collaborations or professional opportunities.", "email": "geetagalagali05@gmail.com", "address": "Karnataka, India"}}, {"model": "main.sociallink", "pk": 1, "fields": {"platform": "github", "url": "https://github.com/Geeta1923", "icon_class": "fab fa-github", "is_active": true}}, {"model": "main.sociallink", "pk": 2, "fields": {"platform": "linkedin", "url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/geeta-r-galagali-55a89329595", "icon_class": "fa